      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a dual-VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings, ensuring the communicative handling these M-cars are known for. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The exterior finish and Nappa leather interior are in concours condition, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and fastidious mechanical stewardship.",
